{"tid":2352584,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國新一屆國會 裴洛西以7票之差成功續任眾院議長","createTime":"2021-01-04T06:15:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T11:37:15.000Z","uid":78519,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e323e17e7f2e180ec7748b68a99b8a9976dcdb63","tid":2352584,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T06:15:34.000Z","msg":"（法新社華盛頓3日電） 美國新一屆國會的議員今天宣誓就任後，民主黨籍的聯邦眾議院議長裴洛西獲得216票支持，勝過共和黨眾議員麥卡錫的209票，裴洛西以極小差距續任議長。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨在去年11月美國大選丟失眾院11席，新一屆國會剩下222席眾議員，共和黨則增加到211席。<br />\n<br />\n但因為部分民主黨議員跑票，裴洛西（Nancy Pelosi）今天獲得216票支持，險勝共和黨對手麥卡錫（Kevin McCarthy）的209票。<br />\n<br />\n現年80歲的裴洛西再度獲得眾議員支持後，這是她第4度出任眾議院議長。（譯者：陳彥鈞）"},{"pid":"2493e74bde655c8f0bfb59e5968817b6a9151fdd","tid":2352584,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T06:17:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a22fb87c5539c93ee03fe4bf72d1c4e6eb2780","tid":2352584,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T06:19:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14502c7af75a8f257749c2e5f184dedc18ba185f","tid":2352584,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T06:26:41.000Z","msg":"你話如果10個倒戈，GOP就控制到"},{"pid":"78dbc312cb195177e07f5597a891ba9545691f23","tid":2352584,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T06:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8715c51bf11f3b7b09dc7a9ebb1eba3a58ed2bc","tid":2352584,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T06:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.g